<TitleBar>
  <h1 class="title text-white text-lg flex-1">
    About
  </h1>
</TitleBar>

<div class="about p-4 flex-1 w-full h-full overflow-auto">
  <p class="pb-4">
    Davros is a fully <a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" href="https://github.com/mnutt/davros/blob/master/LICENSE">open source</a> file storage platform, built specifically to run inside of Sandstorm. It allows you to store files on your Sandstorm server, and optionally sync them among many desktop clients.
  </p>

  <p class="pb-4">
    We welcome contributions! <a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" href="https://github.com/mnutt/davros">Fork Davros on Github</a> and open a pull request.
  </p>

  <h2 class="font-bold text-lg mt-2 pb-4">Software Powering Davros</h2>

  <ul class="list-disc list-inside px-2 pb-4">
    <li><a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" href="http://emberjs.com/">Ember.js</a> is a client-side MVC framework that enables all of the javascript interactions.</li>
    <li><a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" href="https://github.com/mikedeboer/jsDAV">jsDAV</a> handles server-side syncing of files to clients.</li>
    <li><a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" href="https://nodejs.org">Node.js</a> runs the backend.</li>
    <li><a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" href="https://sandstorm.io">Sandstorm</a> handles user authentication, sharing, and keeping the apps in line.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2 class="font-bold text-lg mt-2 pb-4">Release Notes</h2>

  <em>Note: this list only shows up to the release you are currently using. You can find out if there is a newer release by clicking on the notifications icon in the Sandstorm bar.</em>

  <div class="changelog my-4">
    <MarkdownToHtml @markdown={{this.model}} />
  </div>
</div>
